---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Legal Information</h1>

<section class="mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>
  <div class="text-gray-400">
    <p class="mb-4">
      This website respects your privacy. No personal data is collected, stored,
      or shared.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
      <li>No cookies are used.</li>
      <li>IP addresses are not stored.</li>
      <li>No tracking or profiling is performed.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Anonymous analytics are used solely to understand general traffic and page
      usage (e.g., number of visits, popular pages). These analytics do not
      collect personal information and are fully anonymized.
    </p>
    <p>
      By browsing this site, you agree to this privacy approach. If you have any
      questions, feel free to contact me.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mb-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h2>
  <div class="text-gray-400">
    <p class="mb-4">
      By accessing this website, you agree to use it responsibly and for
      informational purposes only.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      All content, projects, and materials shared here are provided "as is",
      without warranties or guarantees. You are free to explore, learn, and take
      inspiration, but please do not copy or redistribute content without
      permission.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site does not offer any services, commercial transactions, or user
      accounts. I reserve the right to update content, structure, or policies at
      any time without prior notice.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="pt-8 text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
  © {year} All rights reserved.
</footer>
